mar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and the best after him is Umar. Then, Allah will place goodness wherever He wishes.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 922 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":20492,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26550,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/20\/abu-bakr-on-custody-a-divorced-mother-has-more-right-to-her-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":20492,"position":2},"title":"Abu Bakr on Custody: A divorced mother has more right to her children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 20, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qasim ibn Muhammad reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab had married a woman of the Ansar and she gave birth to \u2018Asim ibn Umar, then he divorced her. Umar came to Quba\u2019 and he found his son \u2018Asim playing in the courtyard of the mosque. He took him by the arm and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":20492,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":20492,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":f